reviewText: Being searching for this movie for sometime, and pleased too have purchased it. This movie is one of those classic comedies that I find myself always laughing.
I LOVE THIS MOVIE TOO HAPPY I FOUND IT
One of the funniest movies ever made!!!!!
I like this movie very much. I was so happy when I found it here. This is a must see movie.
It was funny as hell... It was real comedy.. Tommy Davidson was really funny.. The story line was very excellent
this movie is hard to find it was not given the chance at theater or on DVD. Tommy Davidson and Larry Miller are  off the charts with an excellent writing storyline and comedy was funny
Great Movie! Great Acting! Great Comedy!
